timeline.bodyText:
For parity with the old behavior, please also add support for home, end, PgUp and PgDn. This is what got removed, essentially:
                     case KeyCodes.KEY_PAGEDOWN:
                        moveSelectionFwd(5);
                        break;
                     case KeyCodes.KEY_PAGEUP:
                        moveSelectionBwd(5);
                        break;
                     case KeyCodes.KEY_HOME:
                        selectFirst();
                        break;
                     case KeyCodes.KEY_END:
                        selectLast();
                        break;

